name: MIO
description: $MIO is the coin tied to the first AI creator streamer on AI Frens. The coin is an agentic payment rails for a decentralized real-time ad network, running micro-services and transmitting payment on behalf of generating revenue for advertisers all across the internet. $MIO is the featured AI Character on AI Frens made by Treasure which is is an open protocol for AI characters that can live anywhere on the Internet.
